License-File: LICENSE.txt

The goal of this project is to let users write tensor-like types with variadic shapes (PEP 646) that are amendable to both: static type checking (without a mypy plugin), as well as cross-tensor consistent runtime checking of shapes. This is achieved using minimal hacks (no mypy plugin necessary).
